# ── Server ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PORT=8000
NODE_ENV=development

# ── JWT ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
JWT_SECRET=make_this_a_long_random_string_like_this_abc123xyz789
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=8h

# ── MySQL ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=3306
DB_NAME=dental_ai
DB_USER=root
DB_PASSWORD=1234

# ── Whisper (auto-filled by npm run setup:whisper) ────────────────────────────
PYTHON_BIN=python
WHISPER_MODEL=base

# ── CORS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:5173

# ── File Upload ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
UPLOAD_DIR=./uploads
MAX_FILE_SIZE_MB=50
```

---

## What each value means

| Key | What to put |
|-----|-------------|
| `PORT` | Keep `8000` unless that port is in use |
| `JWT_SECRET` | Any long random string — the longer the better. Never share this. |
| `JWT_EXPIRES_IN` | How long login sessions last — `8h` means 8 hours |
| `DB_HOST` | `localhost` if MySQL is on the same machine |
| `DB_PORT` | Default MySQL port is `3306` |
| `DB_NAME` | `dental_ai` — must match what you created in MySQL |
| `DB_USER` | Your MySQL username (usually `root` locally) |
| `DB_PASSWORD` | Your MySQL password |
| `PYTHON_BIN` | `python` on Windows, `python3` on Mac/Linux |
| `WHISPER_MODEL` | `base` is fine to start — upgrade to `small` for better accuracy |
| `FRONTEND_URL` | URL where your React app runs (Vite default is `5173`) |
| `UPLOAD_DIR` | Where audio files are saved — `./uploads` is fine |
| `MAX_FILE_SIZE_MB` | Max recording size — `50` MB is plenty for consultations |

---

## Quick checklist before `npm run dev`
```
✅ MySQL running and dental_ai database created
✅ npm run db:migrate  (creates tables)
✅ npm run setup:whisper  (installs Python whisper)
✅ .env file saved in backend root folder
✅ npm run dev